Subject: Re: [T2] Rear Brake Hose installation

Follow the metal lines that leave the top middle of the brake drum backing plate. Next to the bleeder screw. Follow the metal lines and you will find the rubber lines at the point where the suspension moves. Yes, not an easy job but quite important. 

Chris
